[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Founding)</fld> <def>The aperture in a mold for
pouring in the metal; the gate.</def> <rj><au>Simmonds.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ingathering</ent>⟦br⟧
